  fix QA warnings. Fix various ebuild issues in 1.1. Add gettext and
  pkg-config in DEPEND per bug #233070.

  02 Jul 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> blogtk-1.0.ebuild,
  blogtk-1.1.ebuild:
