*blogtk-1.1 (16 Jan 2005)

  16 Jan 2005; Gustavo Felisberto <humpback@gentoo.org>; metadata.xml,
  -blogtk-0.8.ebuild, -blogtk-0.9.ebuild, blogtk-1.0.ebuild,
  +blogtk-1.1.ebuild:
  Marked 1.0 x86, removed older versions, fixed date on 1.0 and added 1.1 that
  closes bug 78166, thanks to Jason Oliveira for bringing this to our attention.
  also added myself as maintainer in metadata.xml

  14 Oct 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> blogtk-1.0.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

